---
// About section - telling Dain's story
---

<section id="about" class="section bg-brand-slate text-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
      
      <!-- Image / Visual -->
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="aspect-square bg-brand-navy rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
          <!-- Placeholder for Dain's photo -->
          <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
            <div class="text-center">
              <span class="text-8xl">🦈</span>
              <p class="mt-4 text-brand-silver text-sm">Owner photo coming soon</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Experience Badge -->
        <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-6 bg-orange-500 text-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-xl">
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold">10+</div>
          <div class="text-sm">Years Experience</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Content -->
      <div>
        <span class="text-orange-400 font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">About Hammerhead</span>
        <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold">
          Fair Pricing. Quality Work. No BS.
        </h2>
        
        <div class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-gray-300">
          <p>
            I'm Dain Cox, and I've been pouring concrete for over a decade. I started Hammerhead Concrete 
            because I was tired of seeing homeowners get overcharged by contractors who take advantage 
            of the fact that most people don't know what concrete should cost.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong class="text-white">My promise is simple:</strong> transparent, itemized pricing on every job. 
            You'll know exactly what you're paying for — the concrete, the labor, the materials. No hidden fees, 
            no surprises, no games.
          </p>
          <p>
            I take pride in doing things right. That means proper prep work, quality materials, and finishes 
            that last. In 10+ years of work, I've never had a single complaint. That's not luck — that's 
            attention to detail.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Key Points -->
        <div class="mt-8 grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-white/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-orange-400" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-white">Zero Complaints</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Over a decade of happy customers</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-white/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-orange-400" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.05 4.05a7 7 0 119.9 9.9L10 18.9l-4.95-4.95a7 7 0 010-9.9zM10 11a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-white">Locally Owned</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Serving Brown County & beyond</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-white/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-orange-400" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                <path d="M4 4a2 2 0 00-2 2v4a2 2 0 002 2V6h10a2 2 0 00-2-2H4zm2 6a2 2 0 012-2h8a2 2 0 012 2v4a2 2 0 01-2 2H8a2 2 0 01-2-2v-4zm6 4a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-white">Transparent Pricing</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Itemized quotes, no surprises</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-white/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-orange-400" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M6 6V5a3 3 0 013-3h2a3 3 0 013 3v1h2a2 2 0 012 2v3.57A22.952 22.952 0 0110 13a22.95 22.95 0 01-8-1.43V8a2 2 0 012-2h2zm2-1a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v1H8V5zm1 5a1 1 0 011-1h.01a1 1 0 110 2H10a1 1 0 01-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-white">Fully Equipped</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">All tools and equipment on-site</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- CTA -->
        <div class="mt-10">
          <a href="tel:+13254308305" class="btn-primary text-lg px-8 py-4">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z" />
            </svg>
            Call Dain: (325) 430-8305
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
